 or waitlist policy enforced&#xa;• Payment must be verified before approval&#xa;• Completion requires attendance, assessment, and financial clearance" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FAFAFA;strokeColor=#757575;fontFamily=Arial;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="250" width="350" height="185" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="note2" value="Access Rule:&#xa;Only Active enrollment enables learning resources,&#xa;attendance, and assessment access." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FAFAFA;strokeColor=#757575;fontFamily=Arial;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="500" width="350" height="105" as="geometry"/></mxCell></root></mxGraphModel></diagram></mxfile>